---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About — Lynn Baxter">
  <main class="container about">
    <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
    <img class="portrait" src="/assets/portrait.png" alt="Lynn Baxter" width="120" height="120" />
    <div class="prose">
      <p class="lead">I build tools for families and test them on mine.</p>
      <p>
        I design for childhood, care, and coordination &mdash; problems usually filed
        under <em>soft</em>. They aren&rsquo;t: a child&rsquo;s medical information is a
        distributed-systems problem, and a household is an operations problem. I take them
        seriously, build the real thing, and keep honest notes on what fails. The case studies
        here are those notes.
      </p>
      <p>
        The route: a biology degree from San Francisco State. Nine years running offices and
        facilities for San Francisco startups &mdash; Slack, Blend &mdash; keeping buildings and
        three hundred people&rsquo;s days working. UX retraining at BloomTech after a 2019 layoff.
        Two years of freelance product design for fintech and marketplace clients. A decade of
        narrating and producing audiobooks, two published titles. Four kids.
      </p>
      <p>
        Currently: rebuilding Kiddex around one idea &mdash; enter it once. Designing a
        childcare/coworking space. Early-childhood-education coursework at Berkeley City College.
      </p>
      <p>
        Albany, California. A blended household of three adults and three kids.
      </p>
    </div>
  </main>

  <style>
    .about { padding-block: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 3rem) clamp(3rem, 8vw, 4rem); max-width: 680px; }
    .portrait { width: 120px; height: 120px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover; margin: 1rem 0 2rem; }
    .prose .lead {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 1.2rem + 1.9vw, 2.1rem);
      font-weight: 500;
      line-height: 1.15;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      margin: 0 0 1.5rem;
    }
    .prose p { font-size: clamp(1.05rem, 1rem + 0.35vw, 1.15rem); line-height: 1.7; margin: 0 0 1.3rem; max-width: 60ch; color: var(--color-ink); }
    .prose em { font-style: italic; color: var(--color-clay); }
  </style>
</Base>
